ZH: 我把本子挂在墙上。
EN: I hang the notebook on the wall.
ZH: 妈妈把衣服挂在晾衣架上。
EN: Mom hangs the clothes on the clothesline.
ZH: 他把手机挂在腰间。
EN: He hangs his phone on his waist.
ZH: 她把项链挂在颈部。
EN: She hangs the necklace around her neck.
ZH: 我把钥匙挂在钥匙链上。
EN: I hang the keys on the keychain.
ZH: 他喜欢把中文词典挂在书架上。
EN: He likes to hang the Chinese dictionary on the bookshelf.
ZH: 我常常把围巾挂在门旁边。
EN: I often hang the scarf by the door.
ZH: 她把徽章挂在胸前。
EN: She hangs the badge on her chest.
ZH: 他挂在鼻上的眼镜经常摔。
EN: The glasses hanging on his nose often fall.
ZH: 我挂在脖子上的手表是送给我的礼物。
EN: The watch I hang around my neck was a gift.
ZH: 请你把外套挂在衣架上。
EN: Please hang your coat on the hanger.
ZH: 她把帽子挂在门把手上。
EN: She hangs her hat on the doorknob.
ZH: 我们把画挂在客厅的墙上。
EN: We hang the painting on the living room wall.
ZH: 这间教室挂在楼下的走廊。
EN: This classroom hangs on the corridor downstairs.
ZH: 他希望能挂在名校的墙上毕业照上。
EN: He hopes to hang his graduation photo on the wall of a prestigious school.
ZH: 喜欢园艺的人常常把水壶挂在园架上。
EN: people who enjoy gardening often hang a water pot on the garden rack.
ZH: 她把吉他挂在肩上。
EN: She hangs the guitar on her shoulder.
ZH: 他喜欢把照片挂在卧室的墙上。
EN: He likes to hang photos on the walls of his bedroom.
ZH: 妹妹总是把气球挂在自行车上。
EN: My younger sister always hangs balloons on her bicycle.
ZH: 爷爷喜欢把锣挂在院子的树枝上。
EN: Grandpa likes to hang gongs on the branches in the yard.
ZH: 她把饰品挂在包包上。
EN: She hangs accessories on her bag.
